sequenceDiagram
    participant KFTO as Kubeflow Training Operator<br/>Kubernetes API<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant AccLaunch as accelerate_launch.py<br/>Container Entry Point
    participant SFTTrainer as sft_trainer.py<br/>Training Orchestration
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant PVC as PersistentVolumeClaim<br/>Filesystem
    participant GPU as NVIDIA GPU<br/>PCIe/NVLink
    participant FSDPWorker as FSDP Workers<br/>29500/TCP<br/>plaintext
    participant Tracker as MLflow/Aim/ClearML<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>configurable

    Note over KFTO,Tracker: Flow 1: Training Job Execution

    KFTO->>AccLaunch: Create PyTorchJob Pod<br/>ServiceAccount auth
    activate AccLaunch

    AccLaunch->>AccLaunch: Parse JSON config<br/>(SFT_TRAINER_CONFIG_JSON_PATH)
    AccLaunch->>AccLaunch: Auto-detect GPU count<br/>(torch.cuda.device_count)
    AccLaunch->>AccLaunch: Apply FSDP defaults

    AccLaunch->>SFTTrainer: Initialize training<br/>(in-process call)
    activate SFTTrainer

    SFTTrainer->>HFHub: Download model & tokenizer<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token (HF_TOKEN)
    HFHub-->>SFTTrainer: Model weights + tokenizer files

    SFTTrainer->>PVC: Read training data<br/>(/data/input, POSIX permissions)
    PVC-->>SFTTrainer: Dataset (JSON/JSONL/Arrow/Parquet)

    SFTTrainer->>SFTTrainer: Tokenize & preprocess data<br/>(DataPreProcessor handler chain)

    SFTTrainer->>SFTTrainer: Initialize SFTTrainer<br/>(PEFT config: LoRA/QLoRA/PromptTuning)

    loop Training Loop (per epoch)
        SFTTrainer->>GPU: Forward pass<br/>(CUDA compute)
        GPU-->>SFTTrainer: Loss tensor

        SFTTrainer->>FSDPWorker: Gradient sync (all-reduce)<br/>29500/TCP c10d static rendezvous<br/>plaintext (no encryption)
        FSDPWorker-->>SFTTrainer: Synchronized gradients

        SFTTrainer->>GPU: Backward pass + optimizer step
        GPU-->>SFTTrainer: Updated parameters

        SFTTrainer->>Tracker: Log metrics (loss, lr, epoch)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, URI/API key auth
        Tracker-->>SFTTrainer: Ack

        Note over SFTTrainer: TrainerController evaluates rules<br/>(simpleeval: safe expression eval)<br/>May trigger early stopping
    end

    SFTTrainer->>PVC: Save model checkpoint<br/>(/data/output, safetensors format)
    PVC-->>SFTTrainer: Write complete

    deactivate SFTTrainer

    Note over AccLaunch,PVC: Flow 2: vLLM Adapter Post-Processing

    AccLaunch->>PVC: Read checkpoint directory<br/>(adapter_model.safetensors)
    PVC-->>AccLaunch: LoRA adapter weights

    AccLaunch->>AccLaunch: post_process_vLLM_adapters<br/>(extract new embeddings)

    AccLaunch->>PVC: Write new_embeddings.safetensors
    AccLaunch->>PVC: Write .complete sentinel file

    deactivate AccLaunch
